Recommender Systems:

It is everywhere now. Google recommends something. Same with Netflix, Youtube.

What do they do:
They are various ml algorithms such as supervised learning, classification, hybrid approaches, popular/commonly viewed movies, association rules, nearest collaborative filtering.

Collaborative Filtering:
Two users A and B having different rating and movies. We will search for common views of those two users. Same rating or any parameters would be treated as same users.

It is unsupervised learning solving supervised problem.
